Introduction

AZM, also known as A To Z Music, was a four-member South Korean girl group under INNO-K Entertainment. They debuted on March 2, 2018 with the song E.D.G.E.

Unfortunately as of early 2020, AZM has disbanded silently according to Youkyung.
